# Backend Auth Module

Auth modülü en kritik güvenlik yüzeyi. Her karar deliberate — "basit tutalım" mentality burada geçmez.

## JWT — HS256 Simetrik İmzalama

Algoritma: **HS256** (HMAC-SHA256). RS256 değil — single-backend deployment için operational simplicity.

```typescript
// Access token
const accessToken = jwt.sign(
  { sub: user.id, sessionId: session.id, jti: nanoid() },
  config.jwtAccessSecretCurrent,
  { algorithm: 'HS256', expiresIn: '15m' },
);

// Refresh token (farklı secret)
const refreshToken = jwt.sign(
  { sub: user.id, sessionId: session.id, familyId, generation, jti: nanoid() },
  config.jwtRefreshSecretCurrent,
  { algorithm: 'HS256', expiresIn: '14d' },
);
```

### TTL'ler

- **Access token**: 15 dakika (memory only on frontend)
- **Refresh token**: 14 gün (httpOnly cookie)
- **Session inactivity timeout**: 30 dakika (cron revoke)

### Dual-Key Rotation Window

Signing secret 180 günde rotate. Rotation sırasında dual-key verify:

```typescript
try {
  return jwt.verify(token, config.jwtAccessSecretCurrent);
} catch {
  if (config.jwtAccessSecretPrevious) {
    try {
      return jwt.verify(token, config.jwtAccessSecretPrevious);
    } catch {
      throw new AuthTokenInvalidException();
    }
  }
  throw new AuthTokenInvalidException();
}
```

15 dk window sonrası `PREVIOUS` kaldırılır.

## Refresh Token Family Tracking

Her login yeni family_id oluşturur. Her refresh yeni token (generation++) — eski token invalidate. Eski token ikinci kez kullanılırsa **theft detected**, family revoke.

Redis key şeması:

```
refresh_token_family:{familyId}
  → { userId, sessionId, generation: 5, createdAt, lastRotatedAt }
  TTL: 14 gün

family_revoked:{familyId}
  → { revokedAt, reason }
  TTL: 30 gün (forensic)
```

Theft detection logic:

```typescript
async refresh(refreshToken: string) {
  const payload = this.verifyRefreshToken(refreshToken);
  const family = await this.redis.hgetall(`refresh_token_family:${payload.familyId}`);
  
  if (!family || await this.redis.exists(`family_revoked:${payload.familyId}`)) {
    throw new AuthSessionRevokedException();
  }

  if (parseInt(family.generation) !== payload.generation) {
    // THEFT — old token used
    await this.revokeFamily(payload.familyId, 'THEFT_DETECTED');
    await this.prisma.sessions.updateMany({
      where: { refresh_token_family_id: payload.familyId, revoked_at: null },
      data: { revoked_at: new Date(), revoked_reason: 'THEFT_DETECTED' },
    });
    await this.auditService.log({ action: 'REFRESH_TOKEN_THEFT_DETECTED', /* ... */ });
    throw new AuthSessionRevokedException();
  }

  // Rotation: new tokens, increment generation
  const newGeneration = parseInt(family.generation) + 1;
  // ...
}
```

## bcrypt Cost 12 + Timing Attack Protection

User yoksa bile bcrypt compare çalıştırılır (dummy hash) — response süresi bilgi sızdırmaz:

```typescript
private static readonly DUMMY_HASH = 
  '$2a$12$DummyHashForTimingAttackProtection_aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa';

async login(email: string, password: string, ip: string, userAgent: string) {
  const user = await this.prisma.users.findUnique({ 
    where: { email, is_active: true } 
  });
  
  const hashToCompare = user?.password_hash ?? UsersService.DUMMY_HASH;
  const valid = await bcrypt.compare(password, hashToCompare);
  
  if (!user || !valid) {
    if (user) {
      await this.trackFailedLogin(user, ip, userAgent);
    }
    throw new AuthInvalidCredentialsException();
  }
  // ... success flow
}
```

## Rate Limits (Auth-Specific)

| Endpoint | Limit | Window | Identifier |
|---|---|---|---|
| `POST /auth/login` | 10 | 1 dk | IP |
| `POST /auth/login` | 5 | 15 dk | email |
| `POST /auth/password-reset-request` | 3 | 1 saat | email |
| `POST /auth/password-reset-confirm` | 10 | 1 saat | IP |
| `POST /auth/refresh` | 30 | 1 dk | user |
| `POST /auth/change-password` | 5 | 1 saat | user |

Login için composite limit (IP + email) — custom throttler guard.

## Account Lockout

- `LOGIN_MAX_ATTEMPTS` (5) başarısız deneme → `locked_until = NOW + 15 dk`
- Başarılı login → `failed_login_count = 0`
- Kilitli user login denerse → `AuthAccountLockedException` with `unlocksAt`
- Progressive delay (1/2/4/8 sn) ardışık başarısız denemelerde

## Password Policy

Zod schema (`@leanmgmt/shared-schemas/auth`):

```typescript
export const PasswordSchema = z
  .string()
  .min(12, 'En az 12 karakter olmalı')
  .max(128)
  .regex(/[A-Z]/, 'En az 1 büyük harf olmalı')
  .regex(/[a-z]/, 'En az 1 küçük harf olmalı')
  .regex(/\d/, 'En az 1 rakam olmalı')
  .regex(/[!@#$%^&*()_+\-=\[\]{};:'"\\,.<>/?]/, 'En az 1 özel karakter olmalı')
  .refine((v) => !/\s/.test(v), 'Boşluk içeremez');
```

Ek kontroller (server-only):
- HIBP check (k-anonymity API)
- Son 5 şifre reuse kontrol
- Kullanıcı bilgisi (email, sicil) ile benzerlik kontrol
- 90 gün expiry (setting)

## Guards

Üç guard global:

### JwtAuthGuard

- JWT extract (`Authorization: Bearer ...`)
- Verify imza + expiry
- Revoked token check (Redis blacklist)
- `request.user` payload injection

`@Public()` decorator ile bypass.

### CsrfGuard

- GET/HEAD/OPTIONS bypass
- Mutating request'lerde: `X-CSRF-Token` header == `csrf_token` cookie
- Mismatch → 403 `CSRF_TOKEN_INVALID`

### ConsentGuard

- User'ın `consent_accepted_version_id` aktif consent version ile match
- Mismatch → 403 `AUTH_CONSENT_REQUIRED`
- Frontend bu response'ta `ConsentModal` blocking açar

## Consent Akışı

```typescript
@Post('/auth/consent/accept')
@RequirePermission(Permission.NONE)  // just authenticated
async acceptConsent(
  @Body(new ZodValidationPipe(ConsentAcceptSchema)) dto,
  @CurrentUser() actor,
) {
  const activeVersion = await this.consentService.getActiveVersion();
  if (dto.consentVersionId !== activeVersion.id) {
    throw new ConsentVersionMismatchException();
  }
  
  await this.prisma.$transaction(async (tx) => {
    await tx.users.update({
      where: { id: actor.id },
      data: {
        consent_accepted_version_id: activeVersion.id,
        consent_accepted_at: new Date(),
      },
    });
    await tx.consent_acceptance_history.create({
      data: {
        user_id: actor.id,
        consent_version_id: activeVersion.id,
        accepted_at: new Date(),
        ip: /* from request */,
        user_agent: /* from request */,
      },
    });
  });
}
```

## Password Reset Akışı

1. `POST /auth/password-reset-request` — email alır, token oluşturur, Redis'e hash ile kaydeder (TTL 1 saat), email queue
2. User emaildeki linkten döner, token submit eder
3. `POST /auth/password-reset-confirm` — token verify (Redis), yeni şifre set, session'ları revoke
4. Token tek kullanımlık — submit sonrası Redis'ten silinir

Enumeration koruması: non-existent email için de 200 döner (generic message), Redis'e yazmaz.

## Decorators

### @Public()

```typescript
// apps/api/src/common/decorators/public.decorator.ts
import { SetMetadata } from '@nestjs/common';
export const IS_PUBLIC_KEY = 'isPublic';
export const Public = () => SetMetadata(IS_PUBLIC_KEY, true);
```

### @CurrentUser()

```typescript
// apps/api/src/common/decorators/current-user.decorator.ts
export const CurrentUser = createParamDecorator(
  (data: unknown, ctx: ExecutionContext): AuthenticatedUser => {
    const request = ctx.switchToHttp().getRequest();
    return request.user;
  },
);
```

Usage:
```typescript
async create(@Body() dto, @CurrentUser() actor: AuthenticatedUser) {
  return this.service.create(dto, actor);
}
```

## Session Management

`sessions` table her login için kayıt. Revoke tetikleyicileri:

| Trigger | Revoked sessions |
|---|---|
| User logout | Yalnız mevcut |
| Password change | Diğer tüm session'lar (mevcut korunur) |
| Admin manual revoke | Belirtilen |
| Account deactivate | Tüm |
| Inactivity timeout (cron 5 dk) | Inactive > 30 dk |
| Theft detection | Family'deki tüm |

## Banned Patterns

- `JWT_SECRET` hardcode (env var zorunlu)
- Access token localStorage/sessionStorage (memory only — frontend kuralı ama backend'in response'u bunu destekler)
- `bcrypt.compare` short-circuit (user yoksa bile çalışır)
- Generic "Invalid" error (typed exception)
- `jwt.decode()` verify yerine (hiçbir zaman!)
- Password log'lama (Pino redaction)
- Session expiry'i token expiry'e bağlama (sessions table kendi lifecycle)

